---
import Layout from "@/layout/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Megumi Kato"
  description="Haikel's Wife"
  url="https://megumi.ekel.dev"
>
  <div class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto p-[clamp(0.5rem,1.5vw,1rem)]">
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-full max-w-full">
      <div
        class="border-4 border-[#111] w-full max-w-full bg-[#ffe658] p-[clamp(0.95rem,1.8vw,1.35rem)] text-[#111] shadow-[8px_8px_0_#111] transition-transform duration-150 hover:translate-x-[-3px] hover:translate-y-[-3px] lg:col-span-2 lg:row-1 lg:min-h-[300px]"
        data-reveal="badge"
      >
        <span
          class="inline-block border-[3px] border-[#111] bg-white px-[0.65rem] py-[0.2rem] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em]"
          >MY BELOVED</span
        >
        <img
          src="/assets/katou-megumi.gif"
          alt="Katou Megumi"
          class="mt-3 w-full max-w-[260px] border-[3px] border-[#111] object-cover"
          loading="eager"
        />
        <h1
          class="mt-[0.7rem] text-balance font-black uppercase leading-[0.92] tracking-[0.02em]"
          style="font-size: clamp(2rem,6.6vw,5.7rem)"
          data-reveal="heading"
        >
          <span class="reveal-word-mask"
            ><span class="reveal-word-inner">MEGUMI</span></span
          ><br />
        </h1>
        <p
          class="mt-3 font-bold leading-[1.45]"
          style="font-size: clamp(0.95rem,1.65vw,1.1rem)"
        >
          It's not like I want something like a confession. I'm fine with a
          chance to fall in love, just a little. I just want simple, casual
          words. Words that can make one say, "ah, so I could fall in love just
          like that&hellip;"
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section
      class="portal-intro relative mt-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem)]"
      data-reveal="portal"
    >
      <div class="portal-pin relative h-[220vh]">
        <div class="portal-sticky sticky top-0 h-screen w-full overflow-hidden">
          <div
            class="portal-content absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-6 bg-[#ffe658]"
          >
            <span
              class="inline-block border-[3px] border-[#111] bg-white px-[0.65rem] py-[0.2rem] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[#111]"
              >Our Story</span
            >
            <h2
              class="mt-5 font-black uppercase leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter text-[#111]"
              style="font-size: clamp(2.4rem,8vw,7rem)"
            >
              Every Moment<br />With You
            </h2>
            <p
              class="mt-5 max-w-xl font-bold text-[#111]/70"
              style="font-size: clamp(0.95rem,1.5vw,1.05rem)"
            >
              Eight quiet chapters. One girl who rewrote the color of my days.
            </p>
          </div>

          <svg
            class="portal-overlay absolute inset-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none"
            viewBox="0 0 100 100"
            preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <defs>
              <mask
                id="portalHeartMask"
                maskUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
                x="0"
                y="0"
                width="100"
                height="100"
              >
                <rect width="100" height="100" fill="white"></rect>
                <g
                  id="portalHeartCut"
                  transform="translate(50 50) scale(0.001)"
                >
                  <path
                    d="M0,-14 C-18,-38 -46,-22 -46,4 C-46,28 -20,44 0,60 C20,44 46,28 46,4 C46,-22 18,-38 0,-14 Z"
                    fill="black"></path>
                </g>
              </mask>
            </defs>
            <rect
              width="100"
              height="100"
              fill="#111"
              mask="url(#portalHeartMask)"></rect>
          </svg>

          <div
            id="portalBrand"
            class="portal-brand absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none"
          >
            <span
              class="text-[0.65rem] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#ffe658]"
              >M &hearts; H</span
            >
          </div>

          <div
            id="portalCue"
            class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bottom-6 text-[0.6rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[#ffe658]/70"
          >
            Scroll to open &darr;
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem)]" data-reveal="journey">
      <div class="journey-pin relative h-screen">
        <div
          id="worm-progress-badge"
          class="pointer-events-none absolute top-4 right-4 md:top-6 md:right-6 z-20 flex items-center gap-2 border-[3px] border-[#111] bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-2.5 py-1 shadow-[4px_4px_0_#111] opacity-0"
        >
          <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[#e11d48]"></span>
          <span
            id="worm-percent"
            class="font-mono text-[0.7rem] font-black tracking-widest text-[#111]"
            >00%</span
          >
          <span
            class="font-mono text-[0.55rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#111]/50"
            >Journey</span
          >
        </div>
        <div
          class="journey-reveal absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center"
        >
          <div class="relative z-10 w-full mt-6 px-0">
            <div
              class="journey-track relative flex flex-row gap-0 w-max will-change-transform"
            >
              <svg
                id="worm-connector"
                class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 h-full"
                preserveAspectRatio="none"
                aria-hidden="true"
              >
                <path
                  id="worm-path"
                  d=""
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="#111"
                  stroke-opacity="0.08"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                <path
                  id="worm-progress"
                  d=""
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="#e11d48"
                  stroke-width="2.5"
                  stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                <circle id="worm-head-halo" r="22" fill="#e11d48" opacity="0"
                ></circle>
                <circle
                  id="worm-head"
                  r="7"
                  fill="#e11d48"
                  stroke="#fff"
                  stroke-width="3"
                  opacity="0"></circle>
              </svg>
              <div
                class="journey-card relative w-screen h-[58vh] shrink-0 text-[#111]"
              >
                <div
                  class="flex absolute inset-0 items-center justify-center pointer-events-none select-none"
                >
                  <span
                    class="text-[34vh] font-black leading-none text-[#111]/[0.04]"
                    >01</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-[2vh] md:top-[6vh] -rotate-3 w-[168px] md:w-[280px] rounded-3xl bg-white shadow-2xl border border-[#111]/5 p-3.5 md:p-6 flex-col items-center"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/assets/katou-1.jpg"
                    alt="Her World"
                    class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-xl"
                    loading="lazy"
                  />
                </div>
                <div
                  class="absolute bottom-[6vh] md:bottom-0 left-0 right-0 px-6 text-center md:left-[7vw] md:right-auto md:px-0 md:max-w-lg md:text-left"
                >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs font-mono font-bold tracking-[0.25em] text-[#111]/40"
                    >01 / 08</span
                  >
                  <h3
                    class="text-3xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase mt-2 leading-[0.95]"
                  >
                    Her World
                  </h3>
                  <p
                    class="text-sm md:text-[15px] leading-relaxed mt-3 md:mt-4 max-w-[80vw] md:max-w-md mx-auto md:mx-0 text-[#111]/60"
                  >
                    The moment I knew everything was different. A quiet presence
                    that changed the color of my days.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div
                class="journey-card relative w-screen h-[58vh] shrink-0 text-[#111]"
              >
                <div
                  class="flex absolute inset-0 items-center justify-center pointer-events-none select-none"
                >
                  <span
                    class="text-[34vh] font-black leading-none text-[#111]/[0.04]"
                    >02</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-[2vh] md:top-[6vh] rotate-2 w-[168px] md:w-[280px] rounded-3xl bg-white shadow-2xl border border-[#111]/5 p-3.5 md:p-6 flex-col items-center"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/assets/katou-2.jpg"
                    alt="Quiet Grace"
                    class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-xl"
                    loading="lazy"
                  />
                </div>
                <div
                  class="absolute bottom-[6vh] md:bottom-0 left-0 right-0 px-6 text-center md:left-[7vw] md:right-auto md:px-0 md:max-w-lg md:text-left"
                >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs font-mono font-bold tracking-[0.25em] text-[#111]/40"
                    >02 / 08</span
                  >
                  <h3
                    class="text-3xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase mt-2 leading-[0.95]"
                  >
                    Quiet Grace
                  </h3>
                  <p
                    class="text-sm md:text-[15px] leading-relaxed mt-3 md:mt-4 max-w-[80vw] md:max-w-md mx-auto md:mx-0 text-[#111]/60"
                  >
                    Effortless, yet unforgettable. The kind of beauty that
