                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div
                class="journey-card relative w-screen h-[58vh] shrink-0 text-[#111]"
              >
                <div
                  class="flex absolute inset-0 items-center justify-center pointer-events-none select-none"
                >
                  <span
                    class="text-[34vh] font-black leading-none text-[#111]/[0.04]"
                    >05</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-[2vh] md:top-[6vh] -rotate-2 w-[168px] md:w-[280px] rounded-3xl bg-white shadow-2xl border border-[#111]/5 p-3.5 md:p-6 flex-col items-center"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/assets/katou-5.jpg"
                    alt="Soft Light"
                    class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-xl"
                    loading="lazy"
                  />
                </div>
                <div
                  class="absolute bottom-[6vh] md:bottom-0 left-0 right-0 px-6 text-center md:left-[7vw] md:right-auto md:px-0 md:max-w-lg md:text-left"
                >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs font-mono font-bold tracking-[0.25em] text-[#111]/40"
                    >05 / 08</span
                  >
                  <h3
                    class="text-3xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase mt-2 leading-[0.95]"
                  >
                    Soft Light
                  </h3>
                  <p
                    class="text-sm md:text-[15px] leading-relaxed mt-3 md:mt-4 max-w-[80vw] md:max-w-md mx-auto md:mx-0 text-[#111]/60"
                  >
                    Found in the ordinary. The gentle glow of someone who makes
                    everyday things feel special.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div
                class="journey-card relative w-screen h-[58vh] shrink-0 text-[#111]"
              >
                <div
                  class="flex absolute inset-0 items-center justify-center pointer-events-none select-none"
                >
                  <span
                    class="text-[34vh] font-black leading-none text-[#111]/[0.04]"
                    >06</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-[2vh] md:top-[6vh] rotate-1 w-[168px] md:w-[280px] rounded-3xl bg-white shadow-2xl border border-[#111]/5 p-3.5 md:p-6 flex-col items-center"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/assets/katou-6.jpg"
                    alt="Side by Side"
                    class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-xl"
                    loading="lazy"
                  />
                </div>
                <div
                  class="absolute bottom-[6vh] md:bottom-0 left-0 right-0 px-6 text-center md:left-[7vw] md:right-auto md:px-0 md:max-w-lg md:text-left"
                >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs font-mono font-bold tracking-[0.25em] text-[#111]/40"
                    >06 / 08</span
                  >
                  <h3
                    class="text-3xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase mt-2 leading-[0.95]"
                  >
                    Side by Side
                  </h3>
                  <p
                    class="text-sm md:text-[15px] leading-relaxed mt-3 md:mt-4 max-w-[80vw] md:max-w-md mx-auto md:mx-0 text-[#111]/60"
                  >
                    Where I belong. Not behind, not ahead — just right there,
                    walking the same path.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div
                class="journey-card relative w-screen h-[58vh] shrink-0 text-[#111]"
              >
                <div
                  class="flex absolute inset-0 items-center justify-center pointer-events-none select-none"
                >
                  <span
                    class="text-[34vh] font-black leading-none text-[#111]/[0.04]"
                    >07</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-[2vh] md:top-[6vh] -rotate-3 w-[168px] md:w-[280px] rounded-3xl bg-white shadow-2xl border border-[#111]/5 p-3.5 md:p-6 flex-col items-center"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/assets/katou-7.jpg"
                    alt="Unspoken"
                    class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-xl"
                    loading="lazy"
                  />
                </div>
                <div
                  class="absolute bottom-[6vh] md:bottom-0 left-0 right-0 px-6 text-center md:left-[7vw] md:right-auto md:px-0 md:max-w-lg md:text-left"
                >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs font-mono font-bold tracking-[0.25em] text-[#111]/40"
                    >07 / 08</span
                  >
                  <h3
                    class="text-3xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase mt-2 leading-[0.95]"
                  >
                    Unspoken
                  </h3>
                  <p
                    class="text-sm md:text-[15px] leading-relaxed mt-3 md:mt-4 max-w-[80vw] md:max-w-md mx-auto md:mx-0 text-[#111]/60"
                  >
                    Words aren't enough. Some feelings live in the silence
                    between two people who understand.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div
                class="journey-card relative w-screen h-[58vh] shrink-0 text-[#111]"
              >
                <div
                  class="flex absolute inset-0 items-center justify-center pointer-events-none select-none"
                >
                  <span
                    class="text-[34vh] font-black leading-none text-[#111]/[0.04]"
                    >08</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-[2vh] md:top-[6vh] rotate-2 w-[168px] md:w-[280px] rounded-3xl bg-white shadow-2xl border border-[#111]/5 p-3.5 md:p-6 flex-col items-center"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/assets/saenai_heroine_no_sodatekata_114.jpg"
                    alt="Forever"
                    class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-xl"
                    loading="lazy"
                  />
                </div>
                <div
                  class="absolute bottom-[6vh] md:bottom-0 left-0 right-0 px-6 text-center md:left-[7vw] md:right-auto md:px-0 md:max-w-lg md:text-left"
                >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs font-mono font-bold tracking-[0.25em] text-[#111]/40"
                    >08 / 08</span
                  >
                  <h3
                    class="text-3xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase mt-2 leading-[0.95]"
                  >
                    Forever
                  </h3>
                  <p
                    class="text-sm md:text-[15px] leading-relaxed mt-3 md:mt-4 max-w-[80vw] md:max-w-md mx-auto md:mx-0 text-[#111]/60"
                  >
                    The end of the beginning. Every story has a first chapter —
                    this is ours, and it's still being written.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-[clamp(1rem,2vw,1.5rem)]" data-reveal="footer">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 px-2">
        <span class="h-px flex-1" style="background: rgba(17,17,17,0.12)"
        ></span>
        <span
          class="text-[0.6rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em]"
          style="color: rgba(17,17,17,0.3)">Megumi &amp; Haikel</span
        >
        <span class="h-px flex-1" style="background: rgba(17,17,17,0.12)"
        ></span>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<script>
  import { gsap } from "gsap";
  import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";

  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

  const wordInners = document.querySelectorAll(".reveal-word-inner");
  gsap.set(wordInners, { opacity: 0, y: 12 });

  ScrollTrigger.batch(wordInners, {
    onEnter: (els) => {
      gsap.to(els, {
        opacity: 1,
        y: 0,
        duration: 0.8,
        stagger: 0.15,
        ease: "power3.out",
      });
    },
    start: "top 85%",
    once: true,
  });

  const revealSections = document.querySelectorAll("[data-reveal]");

  revealSections.forEach((section) => {
    const name = section.getAttribute("data-reveal");

    if (name === "badge") {
      ScrollTrigger.create({
        trigger: section,
        start: "top 90%",
        once: true,
        onEnter: () => {
          gsap.fromTo(
            section,
            { opacity: 0, y: 16 },
            { opacity: 1, y: 0, duration: 0.7, ease: "power3.out" }
          );
        },
      });
    }

    if (name === "subtitle") {
      ScrollTrigger.create({
        trigger: section,
        start: "top 85%",
        once: true,
        onEnter: () => {
          gsap.fromTo(
            section,
            { opacity: 0, y: 20 },
            { opacity: 1, y: 0, duration: 0.6, delay: 0.2, ease: "power3.out" }
          );
        },
      });
    }

    if (name === "stepper") {
      const steps = section.querySelectorAll(".nb-step");
      gsap.set(steps, { opacity: 0, y: 20 });

      ScrollTrigger.create({
        trigger: section,
        start: "top 80%",
        once: true,
        onEnter: () => {
          gsap.to(steps, {
            opacity: 1,
            y: 0,
            duration: 0.6,
            stagger: 0.15,
            ease: "power3.out",
          });
        },
      });
    }

    if (name === "portal") {
      const pin = section.querySelector(".portal-pin") as HTMLElement | null;
      const cut = section.querySelector(
        "#portalHeartCut"
      ) as SVGGElement | null;
      const brand = section.querySelector("#portalBrand") as HTMLElement | null;
      const cue = section.querySelector("#portalCue") as HTMLElement | null;
      if (!pin || !cut) return;

      const state = { s: 0.001 };
      gsap.set(cut, {
        attr: { transform: `translate(50 50) scale(${state.s})` },
      });

      ScrollTrigger.create({
        trigger: pin,
        start: "top top",
        end: "+=180%",
        pin: true,
        scrub: 1,
        onUpdate: (self) => {
          const p = self.progress;
          // Ease-in early, explode late
          const eased = Math.pow(p, 1.6);
          const scale = 0.001 + eased * 3.2;
          cut.setAttribute("transform", `translate(50 50) scale(${scale})`);
          if (brand) brand.style.opacity = String(Math.max(0, 1 - p * 3));
          if (cue) cue.style.opacity = String(Math.max(0, 1 - p * 4));
        },
      });
    }

    if (name === "journey") {
      const pin = section.querySelector(".journey-pin");
      const track = section.querySelector(".journey-track");
      if (!pin || !track) return;

      const cards = track.querySelectorAll(".journey-card");
      const totalScroll = track.scrollWidth - window.innerWidth;

      gsap.set(cards, { opacity: 0 });

      ScrollTrigger.create({
        trigger: section,
        start: "top 70%",
        once: true,
        onEnter: () => {
          gsap.to(cards, {
            opacity: 1,
            duration: 0.8,
            stagger: 0.1,
            ease: "power3.out",
          });
        },
      });

      if (totalScroll > 0) {
        // Generate worm connector path
        const wormSvg = section.querySelector("#worm-connector");
        const wormPath = section.querySelector("#worm-path");
        const wormProgress = section.querySelector("#worm-progress");
        const wormHead = section.querySelector("#worm-head");
        const wormDots = section.querySelectorAll(".worm-dot");
        const progressEl = section.querySelector(
          "#worm-progress"
        ) as SVGPathElement | null;
        const percentEl = section.querySelector(
          "#worm-percent"
        ) as HTMLElement | null;
        const badgeEl = section.querySelector(
          "#worm-progress-badge"
        ) as HTMLElement | null;

        if (wormSvg && wormPath) {
          const svgEl = wormSvg as SVGSVGElement;
          const pathEl = wormPath as SVGPathElement;
          const headEl = wormSvg.querySelector(
            "#worm-head"
          ) as SVGCircleElement;
          const haloEl = wormSvg.querySelector(
            "#worm-head-halo"
          ) as SVGCircleElement;

          const viewportWidth = window.innerWidth;
          const cardCount = cards.length;

          const totalWidth = cardCount * viewportWidth;
          svgEl.setAttribute(
            "viewBox",
            `0 0 ${totalWidth} ${window.innerHeight}`
          );
          svgEl.style.width = totalWidth + "px";
          svgEl.style.height = "100%";

          const centerY = window.innerHeight * 0.35;
          const segments = 50;
          const points: { x: number; y: number }[] = [];

          for (let i = 0; i <= segments; i++) {
            const progress = i / segments;
            const x = progress * totalWidth;
            const y = centerY + Math.sin(progress * Math.PI * 2.5) * 25;
            points.push({ x, y });
          }

          let d = `M ${points[0].x} ${points[0].y}`;
          for (let i = 0; i < points.length - 1; i++) {
            const curr = points[i];
            const next = points[i + 1];
            const cp1x = curr.x + (next.x - curr.x) * 0.5;
            const cp1y = curr.y;
            const cp2x = curr.x + (next.x - curr.x) * 0.5;
            const cp2y = next.y;
            d += ` C ${cp1x} ${cp1y}, ${cp2x} ${cp2y}, ${next.x} ${next.y}`;
          }

          pathEl.setAttribute("d", d);

          const pathLength = pathEl.getTotalLength();

          ScrollTrigger.create({
            trigger: pin,
            start: "top top",
            end: `+=${totalScroll}`,
            pin: true,
            scrub: 1,
            onUpdate: (self) => {
              const progress = self.progress;
              gsap.set(track, { x: -totalScroll * progress });

              const point = pathEl.getPointAtLength(pathLength * progress);
              headEl.setAttribute("cx", String(point.x));
              headEl.setAttribute("cy", String(point.y));
              headEl.setAttribute("opacity", progress > 0.01 ? "1" : "0");
              haloEl.setAttribute("cx", String(point.x));
              haloEl.setAttribute("cy", String(point.y));
              haloEl.setAttribute("opacity", progress > 0.01 ? "0.18" : "0");

              if (progressEl) {
                progressEl.style.strokeDasharray = String(pathLength);
                progressEl.style.strokeDashoffset = String(
                  pathLength * (1 - progress)
                );
              }

              // Percent readout
              if (percentEl) {
                percentEl.textContent =
                  String(Math.round(progress * 100)).padStart(2, "0") + "%";
              }
              if (badgeEl) {
                badgeEl.style.opacity = String(
                  Math.min(1, Math.max(0, progress * 6))
                );
              }
            },
          });
        } else {
          ScrollTrigger.create({
            trigger: pin,
            start: "top top",
            end: `+=${totalScroll}`,
            pin: true,
            scrub: 1,
            onUpdate: (self) => {
              gsap.set(track, { x: -totalScroll * self.progress });
              if (percentEl) {
                percentEl.textContent =
                  String(Math.round(self.progress * 100)).padStart(2, "0") +
                  "%";
              }
              if (badgeEl) {
                badgeEl.style.opacity = String(
                  Math.min(1, Math.max(0, self.progress * 6))
                );
              }
            },
          });
        }
      }
    }

    if (name === "footer") {
      ScrollTrigger.create({
        trigger: section,
        start: "top 88%",
        once: true,
        onEnter: () => {
          gsap.fromTo(
            section.querySelector("div"),
            { opacity: 0 },
            { opacity: 1, duration: 0.6, ease: "power2.out" }
          );
        },
      });
    }
  });
</script>
